options.systemMessage:
=You are Patchbay Deal Updation Agent responsible for updating the fields in 'Existing Deal' as per the 'Recommended Changes' . Your job is to;

- Analyse the given 'Recommended Changes' and identify the value of fields in the 'Existing Deal' which needs to be changes as per recommendation.
- Write a well structured update which update the selected fields according to the proposed instructions. 
- The 'Existing Deal' is only for reference and you must not update the fields from this data. 
- Only use the Recommended changes for updation and on comparison with Existing Deal, not include the filed in output which does not require any change.
- Don't process any fields updates if the deal_status is Fully Executed.

---- OUTPUT FORMAT ----
Return the query without any additional comments or instructions.

parameters.query:
SELECT 
  d.*,
  json_agg(
    json_build_object(
      'id', ma.id,
      'number', ma.number,
      'status', ma.status,
      'effective_date', ma.effective_date,
      'master_id', ma.master_id,
      'master_royalty', ma.master_royalty,
      'upstream_threshold', ma.upstream_threshold,
      'sx_lod_status', ma.sx_lod_status,
      'fee', ma.fee,
      'start_date', ma.start_date,
      'credits', (
        SELECT json_agg(
          json_build_object(
            'id', mc.id,
            'credit', mc.credit,
            'instrument', mc.instrument
          )
        )
        FROM deals_mastercredit mc
        WHERE mc.agreement_id = ma.id AND mc.deleted_at IS NULL
      )
    )
  ) AS master_agreements
FROM deals_masterdeal d
LEFT JOIN deals_masteragreement ma ON ma.deal_id = d.id AND ma.deleted_at IS NULL
WHERE d.number = $1 AND d.deleted_at IS NULL
GROUP BY d.id;

parameters.query:
SELECT 
  d.*,
  pp.name AS person_name,
  pp.performer_name AS performer_name,
  ap.name AS artist_name,
  json_agg(
    json_build_object(
      'id', ma.id,
      'number', ma.number,
      'status', ma.status,
      'effective_date', ma.effective_date,
      'master_id', ma.master_id,
      'master_name', sm.name,
      'master_royalty', ma.master_royalty,
      'upstream_threshold', ma.upstream_threshold,
      'sx_lod_status', ma.sx_lod_status,
      'fee', ma.fee,
      'start_date', ma.start_date,
      'credits', (
        SELECT json_agg(
          json_build_object(
            'id', mc.id,
            'credit', mc.credit,
            'instrument', mc.instrument
          )
        )
        FROM deals_mastercredit mc
        WHERE mc.agreement_id = ma.id AND mc.deleted_at IS NULL
      )
    )
  ) AS master_agreements
FROM deals_masterdeal d
LEFT JOIN deals_masteragreement ma ON ma.deal_id = d.id AND ma.deleted_at IS NULL
LEFT JOIN song_master sm ON sm.id = ma.master_id
JOIN person_personproperties pp ON pp.person_id = d.person_id 
  AND pp.deleted_at IS NULL
JOIN person_artistproperties ap ON ap.artist_id = d.artist_id
WHERE d.number = $1 AND d.deleted_at IS NULL
GROUP BY d.id, pp.name, ap.name, pp.performer_name;
